text:
Here is the source code showing the bug.
When processing the instruction node in the method "writeNode()":

        case Node.PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION_NODE:
            w.write("<?");
            w.write(n.getNodeName());
            w.write(n.getNodeValue());
            w.write("?>");
            break;

We need to put a space between nodeName and nodeValue.
Therefore, it shoud be

        case Node.PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION_NODE:
            w.write("<?");
            w.write(n.getNodeName());
            w.write(" ");
            w.write(n.getNodeValue());
            w.write("?>");
            break;
